monarchr 0.1.0
  • Reference

    Convert a tidygraph to a monarch_kg graph.

    as.monarch_kg.Rd

    Converts a tidygraph of the appropriate format into a monarch_kg graph. Not intended for direct use.

    as.monarch_kg(graph_obj, ...)

    Arguments

    graph_obj

    input to convert to a monarch_kg.

    ...

    additional arguments to be passed to or from methods (ignored).

    Value

    a new monarch_kg.

    Details

    The monarch_kg class extends tidygraph and defines Monarch-specific methods in addition to functionality provided by tidygraph and igraph.

    See also

    monarch_search.

    Examples

    g <- monarch_search("Cystic Fibrosis", limit = 3)
